text_importexport_label: ukungenisa ngaphakathi kunye nokuthumela ngaphandle iibhukumaki
text_question_merge: Hlanganisa amabhukumaka akhoyo kunye neebhukumaka ezingenisiweyo okanye ubeke endaweni yazo?
text_importexport_content: Apha ungangenisa kwaye uthumele ngaphandle iibhukumaki zakho kwifomathi yeNetscape.
text_help_content1: Umphathi weeNqaku lencwadi sisicelo esinceda ukugcina kunye nokuhlela iibhukumaka ze-intanethi.
text_help_content2: Ukwenza ibhukumaki entsha, okanye ifolda entsha, cinezela i "plus" icon: khetha phakathi kwebhukumaka kunye nefolda, faka isihloko kwaye ekugqibeleni i-URL, emva koko ucinezele ukugcina ukugcina utshintsho, okanye ucofe ukucima ukucima i-bookmark, okanye umva ukutsiba utshintsho kodwa gcina ibhukumaka.
text_help_content3: Cinezela iqhosha elithi "vula" kufuphi nebhukumaka ukuvula i-URL ehambelanayo.
text_help_content4: Cinezela "ukongeza" iqhosha ngaphakathi kwifolda ukongeza into entsha kuyo.
text_help_content5: Kuzo zombini iibhukumaki kunye neefolda, cofa iqhosha u "hlela" ukuziguqula, cofa iqhosha u "buyisela umva" ukutshintshiselana ngesikhundla kunye nento yangaphambili, cofa iqhosha u "qhubela phambili" ukutshintshiselana ngendawo kunye nento elandelayo, cofa u "yiya phezulu" iqhosha lokususa umba kwifolda apho ikhoyo ngoku, okanye cinezela "yiya ezantsi" iqhosha ukuhambisa umlinganiso ngaphakathi kwifolda elandelayo.
text_help_content6: Kwimenyu yezicwangciso, efikelelekayo emva kokucofa i "iisetingi" icon, unokufihla okanye ubonise ukuhlela, intshukumo kunye namaqhosha okongeza. Kuyenzeka ukuba utshintshe ulwimi lomsebenzisi.
text_help_content7: Ukungenisa okanye ukuthumela ngaphandle iibhukumaka, cinezela kwi icon yokungenisa / ukuthumela ngaphandle. Ifomathi yeebhukumaki ze-Netscape ze-HTML ziyaxhaswa, ngenxa yoko kunokwenzeka ukungenisa amanqaku encwadi athunyelwe zizikhangeli zewebhu eziphambili. Xa ungenisa amanqaku encwadi kwifayile, amanqaku ebhukumaki akhoyo ngoku aya kucinywa kwaye abhalwe ngaphezulu.
text_help_content8: Umphathi weeNqaku lencwadi yiNkqubo yeWebhu eqhubekayo, oko kuthetha ukuba isebenza ngaphakathi kwisikhangeli. Xa uyifaka, ngelixa izinto zebrawuza zingaboniswanga, iqhubeka ngaphakathi kwisikhangeli. Amanqaku encwadi agcinwa kwindawo yogcino lwasekhaya lwebhukumaki.marcoparrone.github.io domain. Indawo yogcino isebenza kakuhle kunye nezikhangeli zeChannel, Edge kunye neFirefox. Ezinye iibrawuza zinokucima ugcino lwasekhaya emva kwexesha elithile. I-Android ngokungagqibekanga isebenzisa iChannel, iiWindows ngokungagqibekanga zisebenzisa iEdge. Umphathi weebhukumaki okwangoku akaxhaswanga kwiimveliso zeApple. Ngenjongo yokunceda ukuthintela ukulahleka kweebhukumaka, kuyacetyiswa ukuba wenze ibhekhaphu usebenzisa ukusebenza "kokukhuphela ngaphandle", ngalo lonke ixesha usenza uhlengahlengiso ongafuni kulahleka.

text_about_content4: LENKONZO INGABA NEZINGUQUKO EZIXHASWA YI-GOOGLE. UGOOGLE ULAWULA ZONKE IZIQINISEKISO ZOKUNXULUMANA NOKUTSHINTSHA, UKUCHAZA OKANYE OKUFUNYANISIWEYO, KUFUNYANWA NASIPHI ISIQINISEKISO SOKUCHANEKA, UKUTHEMBEKA, KUNYE NAZO ZONKE IZIQINISEKISO ZOKWENZA UMSEBENZI, UKULUNGELELA INJONGO ETHILE NOKUNGABONI.
text_about_content5: Le app yewebhu iguqulelwe ukulungiselela wena usebenzisa isoftware yokuguqulela exhaswa nguToliko lukaGoogle. Iinzame ezisengqiqweni zenziwe ukubonelela ngoguqulelo oluchanekileyo, nangona kunjalo, akukho nguqulelo ezenzekelayo engagqibelelanga kwaye ayenzelwanga ukubuyisela abaguquleli. Iinguqulelo zinikezelwa njengenkonzo kubasebenzisi bewebhusayithi ye marcoparrone.github.io, kwaye zinikezelwa "njengoko kunjalo." Akukho waranti yalo naluphi na uhlobo, nokuba ichaziwe okanye icacisiwe, yenziwa ngokuchaneka, ukuthembeka, okanye ukuchaneka kwazo naziphi na iinguqulelo ezenziwe ngesiNgesi kulo naluphi na olunye ulwimi. Eminye imixholo (enjengemifanekiso, iividiyo, iFlash, njl. Njl.) Ayinakho ukuguqulelwa ngokuchanekileyo ngenxa yemida yesoftware yokuguqulela.
text_about_content6: Isicatshulwa esisemthethweni yinguqulelo yesiNgesi yewebhusayithi. Nakuphi na ukungangqinelani okanye iyantlukwano edalwe kuguqulelo ayibopheleli kwaye ayinampembelelo yomthetho yokuthotyelwa okanye yokunyanzeliswa. Ukuba kukho nayiphi na imibuzo enxulumene nokuchaneka kolwazi oluqulathwe kwiwebhusayithi eguqulweyo, bhekisa kwinguqulelo yesiNgesi yewebhusayithi leyo eluhlobo olusemthethweni.
